  <div class="box">
    <div class="innerbox2">
      <h4>Key Features:</h4>
      <ul class="outerlist">
        <li>
          <h5>User Authentication:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Secure session-based sign-up and login for all users.</li>
            <li>Only registered users can list properties or leave reviews.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Dynamic Listing Management:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Users can create, edit, and delete property listings.</li>
            <li>Each listing includes detailed info like amenities, pricing, and images.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Review System:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Verified guests can leave authentic reviews and ratings.</li>
            <li>Owners can manage reviews on their listings.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Interactive Maps:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Mapbox integration to view listing locations on an interactive map.</li>
            <li>Helps users find stays in their desired regions visually.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Permissions and Security:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Only listing owners can edit or remove their content.</li>
            <li>Review deletion is restricted to the original author.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="innerbox2">
      <h4>Technologies Used:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li>Backend: Node.js, Express.js</li>
        <li>Database: MongoDB</li>
        <li>Authentication: Passport.js</li>
        <li>Maps: Mapbox API</li>
        <li>Image Upload: Cloudinary API</li>
        <li>Deployment: Render</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="innerbox2">
      <h4>Technical Implementation:</h4>
      <ul class="outerlist">
        <li>
          <h5>RESTful API:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>REST architecture used for clean and scalable endpoints.</li>
            <li>Supports all major HTTP methods through intuitive routes.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>CRUD Operations:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Listings and reviews can be created, viewed, updated, and deleted.</li>
            <li>User interface offers a smooth experience for these operations.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Middleware:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Used for authentication checks, validation, and error handling.</li>
            <li>Ensures secure and consistent app behavior.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Session Management:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Sessions managed via Passport.js and Express.js for secure login states.</li>
            <li>Protected routes for authenticated users only.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Form Validation:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Validation handled by Joi to ensure input correctness and security.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>File Uploads:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Multer manages file input; Cloudinary stores images safely online.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Map Integration:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Mapbox shows listings on a geographic map with clickable markers.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>MVC Architecture:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Follows Model-View-Controller pattern for code structure and clarity.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Backend:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Node.js and Express.js power the backend.</li>
            <li>MongoDB used for storing users, listings, and reviews.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5>Frontend:</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Built with EJS templates, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript for a dynamic interface.</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="innerbox2">
      <h4>Dependencies and Integrations:</h4>
      <ul class="outerlist">
        <li><h5>@mapbox/mapbox-sdk:</h5><p>Used for map functionality.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Cloudinary:</h5><p>Handles image hosting and delivery.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Connect-Flash:</h5><p>For session-based flash messages.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Cookie-Parser:</h5><p>Parses cookies for session tracking.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Dotenv:</h5><p>Loads environment variables securely.</p></li>
        <li><h5>EJS & EJS-Mate:</h5><p>Templates for rendering pages dynamically.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Express & Express-Session:</h5><p>Framework and session handling.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Joi:</h5><p>Used for request validation.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Method-Override:</h5><p>Enables PUT/DELETE in forms.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Mongoose:</h5><p>MongoDB ODM for schema modeling.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Multer & Multer-Storage-Cloudinary:</h5><p>Image upload and integration with Cloudinary.</p></li>
        <li><h5>Passport, Passport-Local, Passport-Local-Mongoose:</h5><p>Used for authentication and session support.</p></li>
      </ul>
